                Water pollution
              </h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                All of the sewage from your house will eventually make its way back into the rivers, lakes and the sea.
                Did you or any other members of your family read a newspaper, use packaged products or 
                eat some fresh fruit? All of these things, along with most other things that you use or eat, also produce sewage in their production.
                The sewage from houses, schools, office buildings, farms and factories contains all kinds of chemicals and materials that are not naturally found in our waterways. 
                <p class="card-text fw-semibold text-decoration-underline">
                  Water pollution | Yarra Valley Water. (n.d.).                </p>
            
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>


